Hendrik G. Meijer: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 24, 2017 4:44 PM ET
Food and Staples Retailing

Company Overview of Meijer, Inc.



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Hendrik G. Meijer  Executive Chairman, Meijer, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships65--
Background

		Mr. Hendrik G. Meijer, also known as Hank, serves as the Executive Chairman of Meijer, Inc. Mr. Meijer founded Meijer Inc. in 1934 and served as its Chairman. Mr. Meijer served as and Co-Chief Executive Officer of Meijer, Inc. until January 1, 2017. Mr. Meijer served as a Director of Fifth Third BanCorp and Fifth Third Bank (Cincinnati, OH) since 2001 until April 18, 2017. Mr. Meijer served as a Director of Old Kent Financial Corp. since 1997 and its subsidiary, Old ... Kent Bank since 1989. Mr. Meijer serves as a Director of Meijer, Inc.Read Full Background




Corporate Headquarters
2929 Walker Avenue NWGrand Rapids, Michigan 49544-9424United StatesPhone: 616-453-6711Fax: 616-791-2572
